b-2a763d216729-4","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_003c3dee-41fa-9c75-baa9-c4fbad9b8ae4_call-17dca814-9258-4c11-acfb-2a763d216729-5","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_003c3dee-41fa-9c75-baa9-c4fbad9b8ae4_call-17dca814-9258-4c11-acfb-2a763d216729-3","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"ws_003c3dee-41fa-9c75-baa9-c4fbad9b8ae4_call-17dca814-9258-4c11-acfb-2a763d216729-6","type":"web_search_call","status":"completed","action":{"type":"open_page","url":"https://www.gvskincare.com/"}},{"id":"tco_003c3dee-41fa-9c75-baa9-c4fbad9b8ae4_call-17dca814-9258-4c11-acfb-2a763d216729-6","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**GV Skincare Center (also referred to as GV Skincare or GV Skin Care Center) in Katy, TX, is a professional skincare and body spa offering personalized facial treatments, body treatments, evaluations, virtual consultations, and professional products.**[[1]](https://www.gvskincare.com/)\n\n**Location**: 23410 Grand Reserve Dr, Suite 302, Katy, TX 77494 (other mentions include nearby addresses like 24551 Katy Fwy).[[2]](https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215)\n\n**Hours** (approximate, based on recent data): Typically Tuesday–Saturday 9:00 a.m.–5:00 p.m.; closed Sundays and Mondays. Confirm directly as schedules can change.[[2]](https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215)\n\n**Reviews and Ratings**: It has an excellent overall reputation, with a **4.9-star rating on Google from 856 reviews** (aggregated via Birdeye). Yelp shows far fewer reviews but includes positive feedback.[[2]](https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215)\n\n**Common positive themes from reviews**:\n- Staff (especially Gaby, and mentions of Maria) are frequently praised for being knowledgeable, professional, patient, caring, and thorough. They provide skin evaluations, explain treatments step-by-step, customize routines, and deliver visible results.[[2]](https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215)\n- Clients report significant skin improvements, such as reduced acne, smoother/radiant/healthier skin, better hydration, and boosted confidence after consistent visits (e.g., facials over months or a year).[[2]](https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215)\n- Specific services like HydraFacials are described as awesome, relaxing, and informative, even for first-timers.[[3]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/gv-skincare-center-katy)\n- Other feedback highlights reasonable prices, excellent care/results, advanced technology/products, and a welcoming atmosphere. Many clients are repeat visitors and highly recommend it (including Spanish-language reviews noting “excelente” results and “100% recomendada”).[[1]](https://www.gvskincare.com/)\n\nThe official website (gvskincare.com) features client testimonials echoing these points, such as radiant skin, professional attention, and long-term trust in the team.[[1]](https://www.gvskincare.com/)\n\n**Note**: While the Google rating is very strong and consistent, always check the most recent reviews on Google, Yelp, or the business’s Facebook page, as experiences can vary. For appointments or details on services, visit gvskincare.com or contact them directly.","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.gvskincare.com/","start_index":253,"end_index":287,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215","start_index":415,"end_index":484,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215","start_index":650,"end_index":719,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-169815982807215","start_index":926,"end_index":995,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://reviews.birdeye.com/gv-skincare-center-1698